{"tid":847697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜貝索斯1600億美元身家 抛離蓋茨居全球首富","createTime":"2018-10-04T11:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T02:04:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6dba1a32fa311e937eee3d721765cee46e2b1c","tid":847697,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"《福布斯》公布本年美國400富豪榜，亞馬遜老闆貝索斯(Jeff Bezos)以1600億美元身家，首次超越微軟創辦人蓋茨(Bill Gates)成為美國及全球首富，是1994年以來第一次易主。蓋茨則以970億美元的淨財富居次席。<br />\n<br />\n「股神」畢非德(Warren Buffett)、社交網站Facebook創辦人朱克伯格(Mark Zuckerberg)及甲骨文創辦人埃利森(Larry Ellison)緊隨其後，居第三至第五位。<br />\n<br />\n其餘位列十甲的包括排第六的Alphabet行政總裁佩奇(Larry Page)、美國共和黨大金主之一的科克兄弟(Charles &amp; David Koch)並列第七位，以及Google創辦人之一的布林(Sergey Brin)和億萬富豪彭博(Michael Bloomberg)。<br />\n<br />\n本年美國400富豪榜的上榜門檻再創新高，達21億美元，上榜者的平均身家為72億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1959084/%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C%E8%B2%9D%E7%B4%A2%E6%96%AF%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%9B%E9%9B%A2%E8%93%8B%E8%8C%A8%E5%B1%85%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1959084%2F%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2581%259C%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258A%259B%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2593%258B%25E8%258C%25A8%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AF%258C&d=z2mhxptcnXvYxAH54PNQzQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=e5c3114a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1959084/%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C%E8%B2%9D%E7%B4%A2%E6%96%AF%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%9B%E9%9B%A2%E8%93%8B%E8%8C%A8%E5%B1%85%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C</a>"},{"pid":"77b446bd5283d9e4fdb90a207f4949feca93f03f","tid":847697,"uid":75462,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"除左因為amzn 股價<br />\n好大原因係bill gate 過去咁多年捐左好多錢/股"},{"pid":"8fb9b0c61e2b78cc07fd4e3a8a48e0eb9